      ) : lang == 'en' ? (
        <div>
          <p>
            Started working at a small startup. I develop complex IT solutions:
            creating web and mini-applications and integrating them with
            hardware. My experience covers process automation in residential
            infrastructure, developing secure solutions for complex network
            challenges, and integrating software with hardware systems. More
            details
