          <ul class="list-disc pt-3 pl-4">
            <li>
              <strong>Languages:</strong> <span>JavaScript, TypeScript</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Backend:</strong>{' '}
              <span>Node.js, GraphQL, Apollo, Prisma</span>
