              day one, shaping its architecture and functionality, as well as
              multiple mini-apps around it.
            </li>
            <li>
              Independently designed, developed, and maintained a highly
              efficient side project, created to scale a future user base of
              140,000+ people.
            </li>
            <li>
              Developed and maintained complex synchronization with the physical
              access control system and other crucial infrastructure components.
            </li>
            <li>
              Diagnosed and refactored inefficient legacy code that caused
              critical failures in the main project, doubling performance and
              ensuring system stability.
            </li>
          </ul>
